527
00:39:50,640 --> 00:39:52,600
I shall inform the general now.

528
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:04,860
Sir, Chief Qiao of the Beggars' Sect and Young Master Murong from Jiangnan are here.

529
00:40:04,860 --> 00:40:07,080
- Send them in now.
- Yes, Sir.

530
00:40:07,080 --> 00:40:10,199
See? Our chief is here to save us.

531
00:40:10,200 --> 00:40:11,239
Indeed.

532
